"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?20/46/21219/abstract/7\">",
"      Walker DH. Rocky Mountain spotted fever: a seasonal alert. Clin Infect Dis 1995; 20:1111.",
"     </a>",
