"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?20/46/21219/abstract/9\">",
"      Strand O, Str&ouml;mberg A. Ciprofloxacin treatment of murine typhus. Scand J Infect Dis 1990; 22:503.",
