"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?20/46/21219/abstract/11\">",
"      Shaked Y, Samra Y, Maier MK, Rubinstein E. Relapse of rickettsial Mediterranean spotted fever and murine typhus after treatment with chloramphenicol. J Infect 1989; 18:35.",
"     </a>",
