"   <div class=\"block mop drugH1Div\" id=\"F171366\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Monitoring Parameters",
"    </span>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:0em;display:inline\">",
"     Triglycerides and other lipids (LDL-C) should be monitored at baseline and periodically. Hepatic transaminase levels, particularly ALT, should be monitored periodically.",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"list fbnlist drugH1Div drugBrandNames\" id=\"F5539860\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
